      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 7,
      "text": "March 14, 1948",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 8,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 9,
      "text": "Mr. Kenneth Wherry",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 10,
      "text": "United States Senate",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 11,
      "text": "Washington, D. C.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 12,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 13,
      "text": "Dear Mr. Wherry:",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 14,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 15,
      "text": "On March 13 at 2:30, M.S.T. o'clock in",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 16,
      "text": "the afternoon I witnessed a strange sight in the",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 17,
      "text": "sky traveling at a very high rate of speed at a",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 18,
      "text": "very high altitude.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 19,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 20,
      "text": "I was first attracted to this sight by",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 21,
      "text": "a noise of motor or whatever it was. It sound",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 22,
      "text": "to me like that of a train rumbling in the distance",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 23,
      "text": "of from 10 to 12 miles on a still day.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 24,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 25,
      "text": "At first glance it looked like it might",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 26,
      "text": "be a vapor trail left by a high flying plane. But",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 27,
      "text": "the white streak that was in the sky never changed",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 28,
      "text": "its shape or did it change in the direction of travel.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 29,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 30,
      "text": "It traveled much faster than any plane I",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 31,
      "text": "have seen traveling in sky high enough to leave vapor",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 32,
      "text": "trail.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 33,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 34,
      "text": "As near as I can describe this sight was",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 35,
      "text": "that it might appear to be a stream lined train",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 36,
      "text": "traveling at a very high altitude at very high rate",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 37,
      "text": "of speed.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 38,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 39,
      "text": "This rocket or whatever it might have been",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 40,
      "text": "was high enough to disappear from sight while it",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 41,
      "text": "was yet very far above the horizon.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 42,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 43,
      "text": "I am not writing this so that it might",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 44,
      "text": "seem to be another disc, fan or whatever you might",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 45,
      "text": "call them. I just saw this and it has been on my",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 46,
      "text": "mind and I thought if there was anything that I",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 47,
      "text": "could be of help to solve this thing I would write",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 48,
      "text": "this to you and you can forward this to the proper",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 49,
      "text": "Dept. if it is necessary. Thanking you kindly",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 50,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
